data.description: Seller is offering a $2,000 Flooring Allowance. Wonderful neighborhood. Pre-inspected. This home offers an open floor plan with cathedral ceilings for a more spacious feel. 3 bedrooms on the main floor. Convenient door joining the primary bedroom to the main bathroom. All appliances included. Downstairs you will find a non-conforming space that could be used as a home office or whatever best fits your needs plus a bathroom. A fenced-in backyard makes this a wonderful opportunity. It is fabulously located within blocks to multiple parks, a short drive to two golf courses and has easy access to the interstate, Offutt AFB, and great shopping and restaurant choices. Get here quickly to make it yours! AMA
